s then saved on a password-protected shared drive accessible to designated staff who require this information to perform their duties. Review the <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/legal/privacy-policy?trk=uno-reg-guest-home-privacy-policy" target="_blank" title="Privacy Policy - LinkedIn" class="ext"><em>LinkedIn </em> Privacy Policy<span class="ext"><span class="element-invisible"> (link is external)</span></span></a>.</p>

